2 Weeks Ago Recall that SaharaReporters had on December 1, 2021 reported how Buhari departed the country to attend the Expo 2020 in Dubai, United Arab Emirates. Shortly after hosting and meeting South African President, Cyril Ramaphosa, Buhari left the nation's capital, Abuja, for the UAE. The Nigerian President has been junketing across the world in the last four months.



